Short Description:
Add cheer to your packaging this holiday season with beautifully patterned Christmas gift bags. These bags feature a fully patterned exterior and interior, spacious side gussets, a white bottom insert for extra support, and coordinating handles. Medium sized gift bags offer a great packaging option for retail product display, gifts, and party favors.
Bag handle types can vary and coordinate with the bag pattern. The Opulent Tree bags have twisted jute handles. The Christmas Town bags have woven cord handles. The Rocking Horse Noel and Holly Tapestry bags have twisted cord handles.

Short Description: Packing List Envelopes:Packing list envelopes are an important part of the shipping process. These envelopes help protect your packing slip in transit, assuring all of the order information is received by your customer. This greatly reduces confusion with orders regarding what has and has not been received. Packing list envelopes feature an adhesive coating or strips for a secure hold. Users simply remove the backing and stick it to the packages, and the adhesive keeps the envelope in place throughout the shipping process.Panel Face Packing List Enclosed:Panel face packing list enclosed envelopes are great for easy identification. The panel easily lets the customer identify that their packing list is inside. On the other hand, the clear facing allows them to see who/where the package is for. Resistant to punctures, tampering and water, you can be assured your document will reach the customer both safely and confidentially.
